# DebOps Project: {{ project_name }}

This is a DebOps {{ project_type }} project.

## Available skills

The following agent skills are installed in `.agents/skills/`:

- **debops-add-host** - Add a new host to the Ansible inventory
- **debops-enable-service** - Enable a DebOps service role for a host or group
- **debops-find-documentation** - Find and read DebOps documentation
- **debops-find-source** - Locate the DebOps source code
- **debops-run-playbook** - Run DebOps playbooks with role targeting

## Safety rules

- Always use `debops check` (dry-run) by default. Only use `debops run`
  when the user explicitly confirms.
- Do NOT modify files inside the DebOps source code.
- Do NOT read or reference files inside `secret/` directories.
- Do NOT prompt the user for passwords - direct them to run the
  command manually.
